      "instruction": "<p>Once the onion has softened, add the <strong>chopped ginger</strong>, <strong>chopped garlic</strong>, <strong>garam masala</strong>, <strong>ground cumin</strong>, <strong>tomato paste</strong>, a pinch of <strong>sugar</strong> and 1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]</span> <strong>flour</strong></p><p>Cook for 1-2 min or until fragrant</p>",
